name: MoeSharpV1
description:
A super model based on MoeDiffusion++_V2 and DreamShaper 3.3.

Just as the other Moe series, it can generate anime style images, but furthermore, now it can also create a photorealistic beauty as well.

For more details, see my hugging face model card.
